title.gco:CharacterString: Digital Map of Village Points of Andaman and Nicobar, India, 2001

abstract.gco:CharacterString: Village points of Andaman and Nicobar linked to Census 2001. Includes data for 547 villages, 3 towns, 2 districts, and 1 union territory. This layer is part of the Village Map of India which includes socio-demographic and economic Census data for 2001 at the Village level.
